{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"06318a82a5","title":"中共中央通知(摘 录)","origin":"根据中央文件的翻印件，翻印者未注明","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"18c179fa2e","index":0,"year":1978,"month":4,"day":20,"articleId":"06318a82a5"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9449ffe6b1","type":"title","text":"中共中央通知(摘 录)","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5"},{"id":"1c8ed6fc51","type":"paragraph","text":"现将《中共中央关于加快工业发展若干问题的决定(草案)》(简称工业三十条)发给你们，请你们立即组织各工业管理机关、各工业交通企业试行。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5"},{"id":"71bcad35a2","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5"},{"id":"f14c221a6b","type":"subtitle","text":"附:","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5"},{"id":"561ca94863","type":"subtitle","text":"中共中央关于加快工业发展若干问题的决定(草案)(摘 录)","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5"},{"id":"bba44c7f33","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5"},{"id":"a754b39dd4","type":"paragraph","text":"二十八、纪律","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5"},{"id":"337cbee57f","type":"paragraph","text":"由于\"四人帮\"的干扰破坏，现在许多方面纪律松弛，无政府主义现象严重，危害甚大。必须加强组织性、纪律性，同一切违反政策、违反制度、违反统一计划、违反财经纪律、违反劳动纪律的现象作斗争。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5"},{"id":"a106a050e6","type":"paragraph","text":"广大职工，都要自觉地遵守纪律，爱护公共财物。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5"},{"id":"e9ed0a0502","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党员、共青团员，特别是各级领导干部，应当成为遵守纪律的模范。要支持和表扬那些认真执行政策、制度和敢于坚持原则的同志，决不允许对他们进行打击报复。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5"},{"id":"08712586ab","type":"paragraph","text":"对违反纪律的人，要进行严肃的批评教育。情节严重、屡教不改的，要给予处分，包括记过、撤职、降级降薪、留厂察看(察看期间只发生活费)，直至除名。除名要慎重。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5"}],"page":{"id":"15b5dae282","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"06318a82a5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}